OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers may linger initially, but will
OL,7,Fslowly fade through the evening to
OL,8,Fgive a mostly dry and fine night.
OL,9,FCloudy across the Peak District, but
OL,10,Fsome cloud breaks soon developing in
OL,11,Fthe east. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FWednesday morning generally
OL,14,Fdry and bright. Thickening cloud in
OL,15,Fthe afternoon brings a risk of rain
OL,16,Flater in the afternoon. Most parts
OL,17,Fseeing some rain overnight, breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
